comments.body: Quote from: robelneo on July 17, 2023, 01:41:42 PMQuote from: SeoOffice on July 15, 2023, 05:38:55 PMRank your website with our Seo office At least, provide us with more information about your service, there are so many SEO services on the internet, it's a competitive industry because every site wants to rank their website but the way you present your service I don't think you know SEO, SEO starts with description if you are that good you will mention your website and describe it in a SEO way.SEO as an industry is quite complex and there are many segments to pay attention to. The offer the OP is making here is extremely frivolous. As far as I've seen, the OP previously offered to set up backlinks on other sites with high domain authority. If the quality of those domains is on par with his presentation here, I definitely do not recommend his service.OP, this is your 4th topic where you offer the same thing. In addition to the fact that it is against the rules of the forum, it will certainly not help you reach clients. But as an experienced SEO marketer, you already know that, don't you?
